{"ID":105,"post_author":"0","post_date":"2025-10-19 22:11:47","post_date_gmt":"2025-10-19 22:11:47","post_content":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div style=\"width: 100%; margin: 0; padding: 0; text-align: center;\">\n<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/10\/downtown2_hero_optimized.jpg\" alt=\"Louisville Downtown Skyline\" style=\"width: 100%; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto;\" \/>\n<\/div>\n<header class=\"hero-section\" id=\"home\" role=\"banner\">\n<div class=\"hero-content\">\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"hero-headline\">Mayor That Listens<br \/>Government That Responds<\/h1>\n<p class=\"hero-subheadline\">\nJoin Dave Biggers in building a Louisville that works for everyone.<br \/>\n Real solutions. Real leadership. Real change.\n <\/p>\n<div class=\"cta-buttons\">\n <a href=\"#volunteer\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">Join Our Campaign<\/a><br \/>\n <a href=\"#plan\" class=\"btn btn-secondary\">See the Plan<\/a>\n <\/div>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/header>\n<section class=\"stats-section\" aria-label=\"Campaign achievements\">\n<div class=\"stats-container\">\n<div class=\"stat-card\">\n<div class=\"stat-number\" aria-label=\"Tech Hub\">Tech Hub<\/div>\n<div class=\"stat-label\"><a href=\"\/policy\/policy-11-technology\/\" style=\"color: inherit; text-decoration: underline;\">Louisville Becomes a Technology Leader<\/a><\/div>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"stat-card\">\n<div class=\"stat-number\" aria-label=\"Worker Bill of Rights\">Worker Bill of Rights<\/div>\n<div class=\"stat-label\"><a href=\"\/policy\/employee-bill-of-rights\/\" style=\"color: inherit; text-decoration: underline;\">$15 Minimum Wage for All Louisville Workers<\/a><\/div>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"stat-card\">\n<div class=\"stat-number\" aria-label=\"Culture Thrives\">Culture Thrives<\/div>\n<div class=\"stat-label\"><a href=\"\/policy\/policy-10-arts-culture\/\" style=\"color: inherit; text-decoration: underline;\">Arts Tourism in Every Neighborhood<\/a><\/div>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/section>\n<section class=\"content-section\" id=\"about\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"section-title\">About Dave Biggers<\/h2>\n<p class=\"section-subtitle\">\n<a href=\"\/policy\/about-dave-biggers\/\" style=\"color: inherit; text-decoration: underline;\">Check my resume, literally and figuratively. Only thing I know how to do is work hard and treat people fairly, how I want to be treated.<\/a>\n <\/p>\n<div class=\"policies-grid\">\n<div class=\"policy-card\">\n <span class=\"policy-icon\">\ud83c\udfdb\ufe0f<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"policy-title\">Louisville Born & Raised<\/h3>\n<p class=\"policy-description\">\n41 years old, lived in Louisville all my life. From Berrytown to Middletown, St. Matthews to Shively.<br \/>\n Family oriented. I may not die here, but I will be buried here.\n <\/p>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"policy-card\">\n <span class=\"policy-icon\">\ud83e\udd1d<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"policy-title\">Community First<\/h3>\n<p class=\"policy-description\">\nRaised in Louisville, Dave knows every neighborhood and listens to every voice.<br \/>\n Your concerns are his priority.\n <\/p>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"policy-card\">\n <span class=\"policy-icon\">\ud83d\udcca<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"policy-title\">Track Record<\/h3>\n<p class=\"policy-description\">\nA lifelong Louisville resident with years of experience serving our community.<br \/>\n Dave understands the challenges our city faces because he's lived them alongside you.\n <\/p>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/section>\n<section class=\"content-section\" id=\"plan\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"section-title\">Our Plan for Louisville<\/h2>\n<p class=\"section-subtitle\">\n<a href=\"\/policy\/our-plan-for-louisville\/\" style=\"color: inherit; text-decoration: underline;\">Bold, achievable solutions to the challenges facing our city.<br \/>\n It's time for leadership that delivers real results.<\/a>\n <\/p>\n<div class=\"policies-grid\">\n<div class=\"policy-card\">\n <span class=\"policy-icon\">\ud83d\udc6e<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"policy-title\">Public Safety<\/h3>\n<p class=\"policy-description\">\n<strong>At least one Mini Substation in every ZIP code<\/strong> - 63 ZIP code areas across Louisville<br \/>\n\u2022 6 officers per station, 24\/7 rotating shifts<br \/>\n\u2022 Officers walking YOUR streets, not just driving through<br \/>\n\u2022 Community knows officers by name<br \/>\n\u2022 5-minute response times citywide<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>12 Community Detectives<\/strong> - 2 per district<br \/>\n\u2022 Dedicated to solving neighborhood crimes<br \/>\n\u2022 Work directly with residents<br \/>\n\u2022 Follow up on every case<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>Results:<\/strong> 20-30% crime reduction (proven in 50+ cities)\n<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"policy-card\">\n <span class=\"policy-icon\">\ud83c\udfe5<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"policy-title\">Wellness Centers<\/h3>\n<p class=\"policy-description\">\n<strong>18 Community Wellness Centers<\/strong> across all districts<br \/>\n\u2022 Primary care (checkups, chronic disease management)<br \/>\n\u2022 Mental health counseling (therapists, psychiatrists)<br \/>\n\u2022 Substance abuse treatment (MAT programs)<br \/>\n\u2022 Social services navigation (benefits, housing, jobs)<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>Affordable Access:<\/strong><br \/>\n\u2022 Sliding-scale fees based on income<br \/>\n\u2022 Accept Medicaid, Medicare, private insurance<br \/>\n\u2022 No one turned away for inability to pay<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>ROI:<\/strong> $2-3 saved for every $1 spent\n<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"policy-card\">\n <span class=\"policy-icon\">\ud83d\udcdc<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"policy-title\" style=\"font-size: 0.95em;\">Metro Employee Compensation Plan<\/h3>\n<p class=\"policy-description\">\n<strong>24% Compounded Raises<\/strong> over 4 years for ALL employees<br \/>\n\u2022 Year 1: 7% raise ($27.4M investment)<br \/>\n\u2022 Years 2-4: 5% annually (compounding)<br \/>\n\u2022 Every department, every position<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>Benefits Package:<\/strong><br \/>\n\u2022 Zero-premium healthcare for all<br \/>\n\u2022 Student loan assistance program<br \/>\n\u2022 Workplace protections<br \/>\n\u2022 Performance bonuses<br \/>\n<br \/>\n<strong>Fair Treatment:<\/strong> Union AND non-union workers\n<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"policy-card\">\n <span class=\"policy-icon\">\ud83d\udcbc<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"policy-title\">Economic Growth<\/h3>\n<p class=\"policy-description\">\nSupport local businesses and create good-paying jobs.<br \/>\n A thriving economy for all Louisville families.\n <\/p>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"policy-card\">\n <span class=\"policy-icon\">\ud83d\udcda<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"policy-title\">Quality Education<\/h3>\n<p class=\"policy-description\">\nInvest in our schools and after-school programs.<br \/>\n Every child deserves the best start in life.\n <\/p>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"policy-card\">\n <span class=\"policy-icon\">\ud83c\udf33<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 class=\"policy-title\">Green Spaces<\/h3>\n<p class=\"policy-description\">\nProtect and expand parks and green spaces.<br \/>\n Healthy communities need healthy environments.\n <\/p>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/section>\n<section class=\"content-section\" style=\"background: linear-gradient(135deg, #003D7A 0%, #002952 100%); padding: 60px 20px; margin: 40px 0;\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center; color: white; margin-bottom: 15px;\" class=\"section-title\">Must-Read Policies<\/h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; color: #FFC72C; font-size: 1.1em; margin-bottom: 40px; font-weight: 500;\">\nStart here: Four cornerstone policies that define our vision for Louisville\n<\/p>\n<div style=\"display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 25px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n<div class=\"policy-card\" style=\"background: white; border-left: 5px solid #FFC72C;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 2.5em; display: block; margin-bottom: 15px;\">\ud83d\udc6e<\/span>\n<h3 class=\"policy-title\" style=\"color: #003D7A; margin-bottom: 12px;\">Public Safety & Community Policing<\/h3>\n<p class=\"policy-description\" style=\"color: #4A4A4A; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\nMini substations in every ZIP code, community detectives, and officers who know your neighborhood by name. Proven 20-30% crime reduction.\n<\/p>\n<a href=\"\/policy\/policy-01-public-safety\/\" class=\"campaign-button\" style=\"background: #003D7A; color: white; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; font-weight: 600;\">Read Full Policy<\/a>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"policy-card\" style=\"background: white; border-left: 5px solid #FFC72C;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 2.5em; display: block; margin-bottom: 15px;\">\ud83d\udcb0<\/span>\n<h3 class=\"policy-title\" style=\"color: #003D7A; margin-bottom: 12px;\">Budget & Financial Management<\/h3>\n<p class=\"policy-description\" style=\"color: #4A4A4A; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\nTransparent budgeting, responsible spending, and strategic investments in Louisville's future. Every dollar accountable to voters.\n<\/p>\n<a href=\"\/policy\/policy-04-budget\/\" class=\"campaign-button\" style=\"background: #003D7A; color: white; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; font-weight: 600;\">Read Full Policy<\/a>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"policy-card\" style=\"background: white; border-left: 5px solid #FFC72C;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 2.5em; display: block; margin-bottom: 15px;\">\ud83c\udfe5<\/span>\n<h3 class=\"policy-title\" style=\"color: #003D7A; margin-bottom: 12px;\">Public Health & Wellness<\/h3>\n<p class=\"policy-description\" style=\"color: #4A4A4A; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n18 community wellness centers providing primary care, mental health services, and substance abuse treatment. Healthcare for all neighborhoods.\n<\/p>\n<a href=\"\/policy\/policy-12-public-health\/\" class=\"campaign-button\" style=\"background: #003D7A; color: white; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; font-weight: 600;\">Read Full Policy<\/a>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"policy-card\" style=\"background: white; border-left: 5px solid #FFC72C;\">\n<span style=\"font-size: 2.5em; display: block; margin-bottom: 15px;\">\ud83d\udcbc<\/span>\n<h3 class=\"policy-title\" style=\"color: #003D7A; margin-bottom: 12px;\">Economic Development & Jobs<\/h3>\n<p class=\"policy-description\" style=\"color: #4A4A4A; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\nGood-paying jobs, support for local businesses, and economic opportunity in every neighborhood. Building a thriving Louisville economy.\n<\/p>\n<a href=\"\/policy\/economic-development-jobs\/\" class=\"campaign-button\" style=\"background: #003D7A; color: white; padding: 10px 24px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; font-weight: 600;\">Read Full Policy<\/a>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;\">\n<a href=\"\/policy-library\/\" style=\"color: #FFC72C; font-size: 1.1em; text-decoration: underline; font-weight: 600;\">View All Policy Documents \u2192<\/a>\n<\/p>\n<\/section>\n<section class=\"testimonials-section\" id=\"testimonials\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"section-title\">What People Are Saying<\/h2>\n<p class=\"section-subtitle\">\nHear from Louisville residents who support Dave's vision for our city\n <\/p>\n<div class=\"testimonials-grid\">\n<article class=\"testimonial-card\">\n <span class=\"quote-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\"<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"testimonial-quote\">\nDave listens to the community and takes action. That's the kind of mayor we need<br \/>\n to bring real change to Louisville.\n <\/p>\n<p class=\"testimonial-author\">\u2014 Sarah M., West End Resident<\/p>\n<\/article>\n<article class=\"testimonial-card\">\n <span class=\"quote-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\"<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"testimonial-quote\">\nHis plan for public safety makes sense. Real solutions, not just promises.<br \/>\n Dave understands what our neighborhoods need.\n <\/p>\n<p class=\"testimonial-author\">\u2014 Michael T., Small Business Owner<\/p>\n<\/article>\n<article class=\"testimonial-card\">\n <span class=\"quote-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\"<\/span><\/p>\n<p class=\"testimonial-quote\">\nFinally, a candidate who understands what Louisville families need.<br \/>\n Dave has the experience and the vision to lead our city forward.\n <\/p>\n<p class=\"testimonial-author\">\u2014 Jennifer L., Teacher<\/p>\n<\/article>\n<\/div>\n<\/section>\n<section class=\"content-section\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"section-title\">Dave in the Community<\/h2>\n<p class=\"section-subtitle\">\nWorking with Louisville residents to build a better future for everyone\n <\/p>\n<div class=\"gallery-grid\">\n<div class=\"gallery-item\">\n<div class=\"gallery-placeholder\">\ud83d\udcf8 Community Event<\/div>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"gallery-item\">\n<div class=\"gallery-placeholder\">\ud83c\udfdb\ufe0f Town Hall<\/div>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"gallery-item\">\n<div class=\"gallery-placeholder\">\ud83c\udfea Local Business Visit<\/div>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"gallery-item\">\n<div class=\"gallery-placeholder\">\ud83d\udeb6 Neighborhood Walk<\/div>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/section>\n<section class=\"signup-section\" id=\"volunteer\">\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\" class=\"section-title\">Stay Connected<\/h2>\n<p class=\"section-subtitle\">\nGet updates on Dave's campaign and find out how you can help make a difference\n <\/p>\n<div style=\"max-width: 500px; margin: 2em auto;\">\n[contact-form-7 id=\"926\" title=\"Email Signup - Homepage\"]\n<\/div>\n<\/section>\n<aside class=\"social-bar\" aria-label=\"Social media links\">\n <a href=\"https:\/\/facebook.com\/rundaverun\" class=\"social-link social-facebook\" aria-label=\"Follow us on Facebook\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><br \/>\n f<br \/>\n <\/a><br \/>\n <a href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/rundaverun\" class=\"social-link social-twitter\" aria-label=\"Follow us on Twitter\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><br \/>\n \ud835\udd4f<br \/>\n <\/a><br \/>\n <a href=\"https:\/\/instagram.com\/rundaverun\" class=\"social-link social-instagram\" aria-label=\"Follow us on Instagram\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><br \/>\n \ud83d\udcf7<br \/>\n <\/a><br \/>\n <a href=\"mailto:contact@rundaverun.org\" class=\"social-link social-email\" aria-label=\"Email us\"><br \/>\n \u2709\ufe0f<br \/>\n <\/a><br \/>\n <\/aside>\n<footer class=\"footer\" id=\"contact\" role=\"contentinfo\">\n<div class=\"footer-content\">\n<div class=\"footer-logo\">Dave Biggers for Mayor<\/div>\n<p class=\"footer-text\">\nMayor That Listens<br \/>Government That Responds\n <\/p>\n<nav class=\"footer-links\" aria-label=\"Footer navigation\">\n <a href=\"#about\">About Dave<\/a><br \/>\n <a href=\"#plan\">Our Plan<\/a><br \/>\n <a href=\"#volunteer\">Get Involved<\/a><br \/>\n <a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy<\/a><br \/>\n <a href=\"#\">Contact Us<\/a><br \/>\n <\/nav>\n<p class=\"footer-disclaimer\">\nPaid for by Dave Biggers for Mayor Committee<br \/>\n \u00a9 2025 Dave Biggers Campaign. All rights reserved.\n <\/p>\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/footer>\n<\/div>","post_title":"Home","post_excerpt":"","post_status":"publish","comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","post_password":"","post_name":"home","to_ping":"","pinged":"","post_modified":"2025-11-06 18:47:06","post_modified_gmt":"2025-11-06 18:47:06","post_content_filtered":"<!-- HOMEPAGE CONTENT FOR WORDPRESS -->\n<!-- Copy and paste this into WordPress Pages &gt; Add New &gt; Set as Homepage -->\n\n<!-- HERO SECTION -->\n<div class=\"hero-section\" style=\"text-align: center;padding: 60px 20px;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #003f87 0%, #0056b3 100%);color: white\">\n    <h1 style=\"font-size: 3em;margin-bottom: 20px;font-weight: 700\">A Mayor That Listens,<br>A Government That Responds.<\/h1>\n    <h2 style=\"font-size: 1.8em;font-weight: 400;margin-bottom: 30px\">$1.2 billion. Same Budget. Better Priorities.<\/h2>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em;margin-bottom: 40px\">46 Mini Police Substations | 24% Compounded Raises for Metro Employees | 18 Wellness Centers | Your Voice in Budget Decisions<\/p>\n    <div class=\"cta-buttons\" style=\"gap: 20px;justify-content: center;flex-wrap: wrap\">\n        <a href=\"#plan\" class=\"button\" style=\"background: #FFD700;color: #003f87;padding: 15px 40px;border-radius: 50px;text-decoration: none;font-weight: 600;font-size: 1.1em\">Read Our Plan<\/a>\n        <a href=\"#volunteer\" class=\"button\" style=\"background: white;color: #003f87;padding: 15px 40px;border-radius: 50px;text-decoration: none;font-weight: 600;font-size: 1.1em\">Join the Movement<\/a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"button\" style=\"background: transparent;color: white;padding: 15px 40px;border-radius: 50px;text-decoration: none;font-weight: 600;font-size: 1.1em;border: 2px solid white\">Contact Dave<\/a>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<!-- SECTION 1: WHY I'M RUNNING -->\n<div class=\"why-running\" style=\"padding: 60px 20px;max-width: 900px;margin: 0 auto;text-align: center\">\n    <h2 style=\"font-size: 2.5em;color: #003f87;margin-bottom: 30px\">Room for Improvement<\/h2>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em;line-height: 1.8;margin-bottom: 20px\">Somebody once said, \"the biggest room in the world is room for improvement.\"<\/p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em;line-height: 1.8;margin-bottom: 20px\">That's how I feel about Louisville. Although we've come a long way, there's still work to be done. I believe with the right leadership we can make significant changes in our community, <strong>ALL<\/strong> of our community, for the better.<\/p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em;line-height: 1.8;margin-bottom: 20px\">Government isn't a marathon, it's a relay. The one that starts the race doesn't finish it, but if we all do our part, we all win.<\/p>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 1.4em;font-weight: 700;color: #003f87;margin-top: 30px\">I'm ready to do my part. Are YOU?<\/p>\n    <a href=\"\/about-dave\" class=\"button\" style=\"margin-top: 30px;background: #003f87;color: white;padding: 15px 40px;border-radius: 50px;text-decoration: none;font-weight: 600\">Learn More About Dave<\/a>\n<\/div>\n\n<!-- SECTION 2: THE PLAN (4-Column Layout) -->\n<div id=\"plan\" class=\"our-plan\" style=\"background: #E6F2FF;padding: 60px 20px\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 1200px;margin: 0 auto\">\n        <h2 style=\"font-size: 2.5em;color: #003f87;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 20px\">Our Louisville Plan<\/h2>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.3em;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 50px\">Same $1.2 billion budget. No new taxes. Just better priorities.<\/p>\n\n        <div style=\"grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));gap: 30px\">\n            <!-- Column 1: Public Safety -->\n            <div style=\"background: white;padding: 30px;border-radius: 10px\">\n                <h3 style=\"color: #003f87;font-size: 1.8em;margin-bottom: 15px\">46 Mini Police Substations<\/h3>\n                <ul style=\"padding: 0;line-height: 2\">\n                    <li>\u2713 Officers IN your neighborhood<\/li>\n                    <li>\u2713 5-minute response times<\/li>\n                    <li>\u2713 Community trust building<\/li>\n                    <li>\u2713 Proven to reduce crime 20-40%<\/li>\n                <\/ul>\n                <a href=\"\/policy\/?search=substation\" style=\"color: #FFD700;font-weight: 600;text-decoration: none\">Learn More \u2192<\/a>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <!-- Column 2: Better Pay -->\n            <div style=\"background: white;padding: 30px;border-radius: 10px\">\n                <h3 style=\"color: #003f87;font-size: 1.8em;margin-bottom: 15px\">24% Compounded Raises<\/h3>\n                <ul style=\"padding: 0;line-height: 2\">\n                    <li>\u2713 $27.4M Year 1 investment<\/li>\n                    <li>\u2713 Retain experienced employees<\/li>\n                    <li>\u2713 Competitive with surrounding counties<\/li>\n                    <li>\u2713 Better employees = better services<\/li>\n                <\/ul>\n                <a href=\"\/policy\/?search=employee+compensation\" style=\"color: #FFD700;font-weight: 600;text-decoration: none\">Learn More \u2192<\/a>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <!-- Column 3: Community Wellness -->\n            <div style=\"background: white;padding: 30px;border-radius: 10px\">\n                <h3 style=\"color: #003f87;font-size: 1.8em;margin-bottom: 15px\">18 Wellness Centers<\/h3>\n                <ul style=\"padding: 0;line-height: 2\">\n                    <li>\u2713 Healthcare in every neighborhood<\/li>\n                    <li>\u2713 Mental health &amp; addiction services<\/li>\n                    <li>\u2713 Preventive care, not just emergency<\/li>\n                    <li>\u2713 Saves $3 for every $1 spent<\/li>\n                <\/ul>\n                <a href=\"\/policy\/?search=wellness+center\" style=\"color: #FFD700;font-weight: 600;text-decoration: none\">Learn More \u2192<\/a>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <!-- Column 4: Your Voice -->\n            <div style=\"background: white;padding: 30px;border-radius: 10px\">\n                <h3 style=\"color: #003f87;font-size: 1.8em;margin-bottom: 15px\">$15M Participatory Budgeting<\/h3>\n                <ul style=\"padding: 0;line-height: 2\">\n                    <li>\u2713 You decide how to spend it<\/li>\n                    <li>\u2713 Direct democracy in action<\/li>\n                    <li>\u2713 Proven in 50+ cities<\/li>\n                    <li>\u2713 Real community power<\/li>\n                <\/ul>\n                <a href=\"\/policy\/?search=participatory+budget\" style=\"color: #FFD700;font-weight: 600;text-decoration: none\">Learn More \u2192<\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<!-- SECTION 3: NOT ME, WE -->\n<div class=\"not-me-we\" style=\"background: #FFD700;padding: 60px 20px;text-align: center\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 900px;margin: 0 auto\">\n        <h2 style=\"font-size: 2.5em;color: #003f87;margin-bottom: 30px\">NOT ME, WE.<\/h2>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.3em;line-height: 1.8;color: #002855;margin-bottom: 30px\">This campaign isn't about one person. It's about <strong>all of us<\/strong> building a better Louisville together.<\/p>\n\n        <div style=\"text-align: left;max-width: 700px;margin: 0 auto\">\n            <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em;font-weight: 700;color: #003f87;margin-bottom: 15px\">Our policies came from you:<\/p>\n            <ul style=\"font-size: 1.1em;line-height: 2;color: #002855\">\n                <li>Mini substations? From neighborhoods tired of long police response times<\/li>\n                <li>Wellness centers? From communities watching neighbors struggle<\/li>\n                <li>Employee raises? From Metro workers leaving for better pay<\/li>\n                <li>Participatory budgeting? From people wanting a real voice<\/li>\n            <\/ul>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.4em;font-weight: 700;color: #003f87;margin-top: 40px\">This is your plan. Let's make it happen.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<!-- SECTION 4: A DIFFERENT KIND OF CAMPAIGN -->\n<div class=\"different-campaign\" style=\"padding: 60px 20px\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 1200px;margin: 0 auto\">\n        <h2 style=\"font-size: 2.5em;color: #003f87;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 50px\">A Different Kind of Campaign<\/h2>\n\n        <div style=\"grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));gap: 50px\">\n            <!-- Left Column: Grassroots -->\n            <div>\n                <h3 style=\"color: #003f87;font-size: 1.8em;margin-bottom: 20px\">The Grassroots Way<\/h3>\n\n                <h4 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-top: 25px\">No Corporate Money<\/h4>\n                <p>This campaign is powered by people, not PACs.<\/p>\n\n                <h4 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-top: 25px\">DIY Yard Signs<\/h4>\n                <p>Don't buy a sign - make one! Grab some cardboard and markers. Get creative. Make it fun.<\/p>\n\n                <h4 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-top: 25px\">Word of Mouth<\/h4>\n                <p>Tell your neighbors. Share with friends. Louisville doesn't need expensive ads - it needs honest conversations.<\/p>\n\n                <h4 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-top: 25px\">Under $3,000<\/h4>\n                <p>We're spending less than three grand on this entire campaign. That's not a handicap - it's a statement.<\/p>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <!-- Right Column: Serious Policy -->\n            <div>\n                <h3 style=\"color: #003f87;font-size: 1.8em;margin-bottom: 20px\">But Serious Policy<\/h3>\n\n                <h4 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-top: 25px\">51 Detailed Documents<\/h4>\n                <p>We're not just talking - we're showing you exactly how we'll do it.<\/p>\n\n                <h4 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-top: 25px\">$1.2 billion Budget<\/h4>\n                <p>Line-by-line breakdown. Every dollar accounted for. Full transparency.<\/p>\n\n                <h4 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-top: 25px\">Evidence-Based<\/h4>\n                <p>Every proposal backed by research from cities where it's actually worked.<\/p>\n\n                <h4 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-top: 25px\">Ready to Govern<\/h4>\n                <p>Not just ready to campaign - ready to lead on Day 1.<\/p>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<!-- SECTION 5: THE NUMBERS -->\n<div class=\"the-numbers\" style=\"background: #E6F2FF;padding: 60px 20px;text-align: center\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 1200px;margin: 0 auto\">\n        <h2 style=\"font-size: 2.5em;color: #003f87;margin-bottom: 50px\">The Numbers<\/h2>\n\n        <div style=\"grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));gap: 30px;margin-bottom: 40px\">\n            <div style=\"background: white;padding: 30px;border-radius: 10px\">\n                <div style=\"font-size: 2.5em;font-weight: 700;color: #003f87\">$1.2B<\/div>\n                <div style=\"font-size: 1.2em;color: #002855;margin-top: 10px\">Total Budget<\/div>\n                <div style=\"font-size: 0.9em;color: #666;margin-top: 5px\">(Same as current approved)<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <div style=\"background: white;padding: 30px;border-radius: 10px\">\n                <div style=\"font-size: 2.5em;font-weight: 700;color: #003f87\">46<\/div>\n                <div style=\"font-size: 1.2em;color: #002855;margin-top: 10px\">Mini Substations<\/div>\n                <div style=\"font-size: 0.9em;color: #666;margin-top: 5px\">(5-min response times)<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <div style=\"background: white;padding: 30px;border-radius: 10px\">\n                <div style=\"font-size: 2.5em;font-weight: 700;color: #003f87\">24%<\/div>\n                <div style=\"font-size: 1.2em;color: #002855;margin-top: 10px\">Employee Raises<\/div>\n                <div style=\"font-size: 0.9em;color: #666;margin-top: 5px\">($27.4M Year 1)<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <div style=\"background: white;padding: 30px;border-radius: 10px\">\n                <div style=\"font-size: 2.5em;font-weight: 700;color: #003f87\">$15M<\/div>\n                <div style=\"font-size: 1.2em;color: #002855;margin-top: 10px\">Participatory Budget<\/div>\n                <div style=\"font-size: 0.9em;color: #666;margin-top: 5px\">(You decide)<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.4em;font-weight: 700;color: #003f87\">No new taxes. No deficit spending. Just better priorities.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<!-- SECTION 6: EMAIL SIGNUP -->\n<div id=\"signup\" class=\"email-signup\" style=\"padding: 60px 20px;background: #003f87;color: white;text-align: center\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 700px;margin: 0 auto\">\n        <h2 style=\"font-size: 2.5em;margin-bottom: 20px\">Stay Updated<\/h2>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em;margin-bottom: 30px\">Join the movement. Get updates on the campaign, community events, and how you can help.<\/p>\n\n        <!-- EMAIL SIGNUP FORM - Replace with actual plugin shortcode -->\n        <div style=\"background: white;padding: 30px;border-radius: 10px\">\n            <p style=\"color: #003f87;font-size: 1.1em;margin-bottom: 20px\"><strong>Email signup form will appear here<\/strong><\/p>\n            <p style=\"color: #666;font-size: 0.9em\">Use plugin shortcode: [dbpm_signup_form]<\/p>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <p style=\"font-size: 0.9em;margin-top: 20px;opacity: 0.9\">We respect your inbox. No spam, no daily emails. Just the important stuff.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<!-- SECTION 7: VOLUNTEER PORTAL -->\n<div id=\"volunteer\" class=\"volunteer-portal\" style=\"padding: 60px 20px\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 1200px;margin: 0 auto\">\n        <h2 style=\"font-size: 2.5em;color: #003f87;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 50px\">Ready to Help?<\/h2>\n\n        <div style=\"grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));gap: 50px\">\n            <!-- Left Column -->\n            <div>\n                <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em;line-height: 1.8;margin-bottom: 30px\">Whether you've got 5 minutes or 5 hours a week, there's a way to contribute.<\/p>\n\n                <h3 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-bottom: 15px\">Ways to help:<\/h3>\n                <ul style=\"font-size: 1.1em;line-height: 2\">\n                    <li>Make DIY yard signs<\/li>\n                    <li>Talk to neighbors<\/li>\n                    <li>Host a small gathering<\/li>\n                    <li>Share on social media<\/li>\n                    <li>Register voters<\/li>\n                    <li>Drive people to polls<\/li>\n                <\/ul>\n\n                <p style=\"font-size: 1.1em;font-weight: 700;color: #003f87;margin-top: 30px\">No experience needed. Just enthusiasm for a better Louisville.<\/p>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <!-- Right Column -->\n            <div style=\"background: #E6F2FF;padding: 40px;border-radius: 10px\">\n                <h3 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-bottom: 20px\">Volunteer Registration<\/h3>\n                <p style=\"margin-bottom: 20px\">Register to get access to:<\/p>\n                <ul style=\"line-height: 2;margin-bottom: 30px\">\n                    <li>Door-to-door talking points<\/li>\n                    <li>Volunteer coordination<\/li>\n                    <li>Event information<\/li>\n                    <li>Campaign updates<\/li>\n                    <li>Training materials<\/li>\n                <\/ul>\n\n                <!-- VOLUNTEER FORM - Replace with actual plugin shortcode -->\n                <div style=\"background: white;padding: 20px;border-radius: 5px\">\n                    <p style=\"color: #003f87\"><strong>Volunteer registration form will appear here<\/strong><\/p>\n                    <p style=\"color: #666;font-size: 0.9em\">Use plugin shortcode: [dbpm_volunteer_register]<\/p>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<!-- SECTION 8: POLICY LIBRARY -->\n<div class=\"policy-library\" style=\"background: #E6F2FF;padding: 60px 20px\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 1200px;margin: 0 auto\">\n        <h2 style=\"font-size: 2.5em;color: #003f87;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 20px\">Explore Our Plans<\/h2>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.3em;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 50px\">We're not hiding behind slogans. Read the actual policies.<\/p>\n\n        <div style=\"grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));gap: 30px;margin-bottom: 40px\">\n            <div style=\"background: white;padding: 30px;border-radius: 10px\">\n                <h3 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-bottom: 15px\">Employee Compensation Plan<\/h3>\n                <p>$27.4M Year 1 investment ($136.6M over 4 years) in Metro workforce. See exactly where every dollar goes.<\/p>\n                <a href=\"\/policy\/?search=employee\" style=\"color: #FFD700;font-weight: 600;text-decoration: none\">Read Full Plan \u2192<\/a>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <div style=\"background: white;padding: 30px;border-radius: 10px\">\n                <h3 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-bottom: 15px\">Public Safety Strategy<\/h3>\n                <p>46 mini substations, community policing, evidence-based approach. How we'll make Louisville safer.<\/p>\n                <a href=\"\/policy\/?search=substation\" style=\"color: #FFD700;font-weight: 600;text-decoration: none\">Read Full Plan \u2192<\/a>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <div style=\"background: white;padding: 30px;border-radius: 10px\">\n                <h3 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-bottom: 15px\">Community Wellness Centers<\/h3>\n                <p>18 centers providing healthcare, mental health, and addiction services. Complete implementation plan.<\/p>\n                <a href=\"\/policy\/?search=wellness\" style=\"color: #FFD700;font-weight: 600;text-decoration: none\">Read Full Plan \u2192<\/a>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <div style=\"background: white;padding: 30px;border-radius: 10px\">\n                <h3 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-bottom: 15px\">Budget Summary<\/h3>\n                <p>Full $1.2B budget breakdown. Revenue, expenditures, every line item explained.<\/p>\n                <a href=\"\/policy\/?search=budget\" style=\"color: #FFD700;font-weight: 600;text-decoration: none\">Read Full Plan \u2192<\/a>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n\n        <div style=\"text-align: center\">\n            <a href=\"\/policy\/\" class=\"button\" style=\"background: #003f87;color: white;padding: 15px 40px;border-radius: 50px;text-decoration: none;font-weight: 600;font-size: 1.1em\">View All Policy Documents \u2192<\/a>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<!-- SECTION 9: SECOND TIME'S A CHARM -->\n<div class=\"second-time\" style=\"background: #003f87;color: white;padding: 60px 20px\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 900px;margin: 0 auto\">\n        <h2 style=\"font-size: 2.5em;margin-bottom: 30px;text-align: center\">Second Time's a Charm<\/h2>\n\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em;line-height: 1.8;margin-bottom: 20px\"><strong>I ran for mayor in 2018 as a Democrat.<\/strong> Did some forums, some interviews. But I've always been an independent - Independent Thinker, Independent Voter.<\/p>\n\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em;line-height: 1.8;margin-bottom: 20px\"><strong>This time, I'm running as an independent<\/strong> because that's what I am. Not anti-Democrat, not anti-Republican. Pro-Louisville.<\/p>\n\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em;line-height: 1.8;margin-bottom: 20px\"><strong>This campaign is different.<\/strong> No big spending. No corporate donors. No political machine. Just honest policy and community engagement.<\/p>\n\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.1em;margin-top: 30px\"><strong>Past campaign appearances:<\/strong><\/p>\n        <ul style=\"font-size: 1.1em;line-height: 2\">\n            <li>KFTC Voter Guide<\/li>\n            <li>UofL\/Forward Radio Forum<\/li>\n        <\/ul>\n\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 700;text-align: center;margin-top: 40px\">Ready for round two. Let's do this right.<\/p>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<!-- SECTION 10: CONTACT -->\n<div id=\"contact\" class=\"contact-section\" style=\"padding: 60px 20px\">\n    <div style=\"max-width: 1200px;margin: 0 auto\">\n        <h2 style=\"font-size: 2.5em;color: #003f87;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 50px\">Get In Touch<\/h2>\n\n        <div style=\"grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));gap: 40px\">\n            <!-- Column 1: Email -->\n            <div>\n                <h3 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-bottom: 15px\">Email Dave<\/h3>\n                <p><strong><a href=\"mailto:dave@rundaverun.org\" style=\"color: #FFD700;text-decoration: none\">dave@rundaverun.org<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n                <p>Want to talk about policy? Have questions? Share ideas?<\/p>\n\n                <p style=\"margin-top: 20px\"><strong><a href=\"mailto:info@rundaverun.org\" style=\"color: #FFD700;text-decoration: none\">info@rundaverun.org<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n                <p>General inquiries, media requests, volunteer coordination.<\/p>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <!-- Column 2: Mail -->\n            <div>\n                <h3 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-bottom: 15px\">Mailing Address<\/h3>\n                <p><strong>PO Box 33036<\/strong><br>\n                Louisville, KY 40232<\/p>\n                <p style=\"margin-top: 20px\">Send letters, suggestions, DIY yard sign photos!<\/p>\n            <\/div>\n\n            <!-- Column 3: Contact Form -->\n            <div style=\"background: #E6F2FF;padding: 30px;border-radius: 10px\">\n                <h3 style=\"color: #003f87;margin-bottom: 20px\">Contact Form<\/h3>\n                <p style=\"color: #666\">Contact form will appear here<\/p>\n                <p style=\"color: #666;font-size: 0.9em\">Use Contact Form 7 plugin<\/p>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n    <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<!-- END OF HOMEPAGE CONTENT -->","post_parent":0,"guid":"http:\/\/rundaverun-local.local\/home\/","menu_order":0,"post_type":"page","post_mime_type":"","comment_count":"0","url":"http:\/\/rundaverun-local.local\/"}
